Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) has issued a certificate of return to Kano state Governor-elect Abdullahi Umar Ganduje for the second term in office.

Ganduje who received the certificate along with his deputy, Nasiru Yusuf Gawna and members of the state house of assembly under the platform of ruling All Progressives Congress (APC).

